pageContext.claim: “Nancy Pelosi needs help fast! There is either something wrong with her 'upstairs,' or she just plain doesn't like our great Country. She had a total meltdown in the White House today. It was very sad to watch. Pray for her, she is a very sick person!”
pageContext.analysis: Pelosi later said Trump referred to her as a "third-grade politician.” Other Democrats heard “third-rate.” She left the meeting. There is nothing to indicate she had a "meltdown."
